description: Demolition of existing buildings and the redevelopment of the site to provide 140 residential units in a mixed use development: erection of a 4/5 storey building on the Parsons green Lane frontage (Block A) comprising retail (A1) or a mix of retail and a restaurant/cafe (A3) at ground floor level (approx 800 sq m) with 32 flats above; the ercetion of a 6 storey building (Block E) to the rear of Block A, comprising 32 flats; the erection of a 4 storey building on the Heathmans Road frontage (Block D) comprising business (B1) floorspace at the ground floor with 16 flats above; the erection of 2 buildings from 5-7 storeys (Blocks B and C) to the rear of Block D, comprising 46 residential units and 14 residential units respectively; together with related open space, landscaping, car parking and servicing
